title: Princess Beatrice and Edoardo Mapelli Mozzi Attend Cheltenham Festival
description: Princess Beatrice and her husband, Edoardo Mapelli Mozzi, enjoyed an afternoon date at the Cheltenham Festival on Thursday, March 14
